abstracts.cdata!:
The proposed credit would assist in
            financing: (a) a four-year (1969-72) highway maintenance
            program, and (b) feasibility studies for about 450
            kilometers of secondary roads, with subsequent detailed
            engineering for about 300 kilometers of high priority roads.
